fields.name: Americano
fields.description: Espresso shots topped with hot water create a light layer of crema culminating in this wonderfully rich cup with depth and nuance. Pro Tip: For an additional boost, ask your barista to try this with an extra shot.

fields.name: Cappuccino
fields.description: Dark, rich espresso lies in wait under a smoothed and stretched layer of thick milk foam. An alchemy of barista artistry and craft.

fields.name: Flat White
fields.description: Smooth ristretto shots of espresso get the perfect amount of steamed whole milk to create a not-too-strong, not-too-creamy, just-right flavour.

fields.name: Mocha
fields.description: Our rich, full-bodied espresso combined with bittersweet mocha sauce and steamed milk, then topped with sweetened whipped cream. The classic coffee drink that always sweetly satisfies.

fields.name: Chocolate Milkshake
fields.description: Our chocolate milkshake is made from whole milk, Cadbury's chocolate powder and a scoop of vanilla ice-cream blended together and served with cream on top

fields.name: Strawberry Milkshake
fields.description: Our strawberry  milkshake is made from whole milk, fresh strawberries and a scoop of vanilla ice-cream blended together and served with cream on top

fields.name: Banana Milkshake
fields.description: Our banana milkshake is made from whole milk, fresh bananas and a scoop of vanilla ice-cream blended together and served with cream on top

fields.name: Cockapoo Cafe Club Sandwich
fields.description: Smoked turkey, Black Forest ham, bacon, sharp cheddar, Swiss, spring mix, tomato, mayo and Honey Mustard on wheat.

fields.name: Cockapoo Cafe Orange and Cranberry Club
fields.description: Smoked turkey, Black Forest ham, bacon, sharp cheddar, Swiss, spring mix, tomato, mayo and with Orange Cranberry Sauce on wheat.

fields.name: Cockapoo Cafe Grilled Chicken Club
fields.description: Grilled Chicken, bacon, sharp cheddar, Swiss, spring mix, tomato, mayo and with Honey Mustard Sauce on wheat.

fields.name: Carrot Cake
fields.description: Giant slice of moist carrot cake with walnuts and cream cheese frosting.

fields.name: Cockapoo Cafe Brownie
fields.description: A moist and rich double fudge treat
